# Pet Vet Coding Puzzles

Browser-based educational coding puzzle game with a block workspace, deterministic execution, SQLite telemetry, and local analytics replay.

## Repository Root
"'`/home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1`

## Prerequisites
- Node.js 20.x
- npm 10.x
- Python 3.10+
- Docker Engine + Docker Compose plugin (optional)

## Environment Setup
```bash
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1
cp .env.example .env
```

## Start Backend (Local)
```bash
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1/backend
npm ci
npm run dev
```
Backend base URL: `http://localhost:3001`

## Start Frontend (Local)
```bash
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1/frontend
npm ci
npm run dev
```
Frontend base URL: `http://localhost:5173`

## Run Tests
```bash
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1
python3 -m unittest discover -s tests -p '"'test_*.py' -v
"'```

## API Contract Summary
- `GET /health`
- `GET /api/levels`
- `GET /api/levels/:id`
- `POST /api/session/start`
- `POST /api/session/end`
- `POST /api/events/batch`
- `GET /api/analytics/dashboard`
- `GET /api/analytics/puzzle/:id`
- `GET /api/analytics/events`

## Docker Compose (Optional)
```bash
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1
docker compose up --build
```

## MVP Constraints
- Exactly 17 playable puzzles.
- On failure, show Oops plus at least one helpful hint.
- On success, complete goal and unlock next puzzle.
- Persist movement and execution events in SQLite.
- Support analytics replay from persisted movements.
