## Troubleshooting

### Backend does not start
```bash
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1/backend
rm -rf node_modules
npm ci
npm run dev
```

### Frontend cannot connect to backend
```bash
curl -fsS http://localhost:3001/health
cat /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1/.env
```
Confirm `BACKEND_PORT=3001` and frontend API base URL targets `http://localhost:3001`.

### Port collision on 3001 or 5173
```bash
lsof -i :3001
lsof -i :5173
```
Stop conflicting process, then restart the corresponding service.

### SQLite reset for deterministic local recovery
```bash
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1
rm -f backend/dev.db backend/dev.db-shm backend/dev.db-wal
```
Restart backend after reset.

