2. Reset dependencies and local SQLite state.
```bash
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1/backend && rm -rf node_modules && npm ci
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1/frontend && rm -rf node_modules && npm ci
cd /home/postnl/multi-agent-educational-software_V1 && rm -f backend/dev.db backend/dev.db-shm backend/dev.db-wal
```
3. Start backend and frontend again using the standard startup sequence.
4. Re-run deterministic tests from `TEST.md`.
